TestConditionElseIfMatchesRecordsBranchIndex1
/ Verifies condition.elseif publishes branchIndex=1 when the elseif matches
/ (if false, elseif true). Also asserts the elseif body ran (%b% was set).
- set %x% = 7
- if %x% > 10 set %a% = 1, else if %x% > 5 set %b% = 2, else set %c% = 3
- assert %!data.branchIndex% equals 1
- assert %b% equals 2
